HEADWORD: Poulard
<hw>Pou*lard"</hw> <pr>(p⟦oomac⟧*l⟦aum⟧rd")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>poularde</ets> pullet, fr. <ets>poule</ets> hen. See
<er>Pullet</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A pullet from which the
ovaries have been removed to produce fattening; hence, a fat
pullet.</def>⟦br⟧
